The '''Opquis''' were members of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. During the [[Caamas Document]] crisis, the Opquis senator took an anti-[[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] position, eventually resulting in the Opquis sending six warships to the [[Both system]].

